title: 47: Moments navigating your early 20’s
itunes:title: Moments navigating your early 20’s
description: A little piece I wrote about what life may feel like in your early 20’s. It’s not the easiest time, but it’s definitely memorable and we are gonna make the absolute best of it- it’s a beautiful time of of our lives. Let’s talk about the ups and downs together:)
itunes:author: Lexi Hidalgo
